721726f-c.title: Manhattan: Morningside Park.
721726f-c.text:
Morningside Park: A series of three views forming a panora-
mic arrangement as photographed from the 110th Street station of
the 9th Avence ''El''. Morningside Drive separates the park from
the Protestant Episcopal Cathedral of St. John ond forms the west-
erly boundary. Manhattan Avenue at the right performs a similar
function.
June 6, 1940
Views 1,2,3
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
